Box data for box_plot, include Value, Level1 and Level2 columns.

box_data.Rd

Box data for box_plot, include Value, Level1 and Level2 columns.

Usage

data(box_data)

Format

Dataframe: include Value, Level1 and Level2 columns.

References

https://github.com/BioSciTools/BioSciToolsDatasets/tree/main/BoxStat/

Author

benben-miao

Examples

# 1. Library TOmicsVis package
library(TOmicsVis)

# 2. Load example data
data(box_data)

# 3. View example data
box_data
